headline: 'Unruly' Trading in China Behind Gold Moves, Bessent Says
summary: Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent blames wild moves in gold prices on "unruly" Chinese trading. "Things have gotten a little unruly in China," Bessent told Fox's Sunday Morning Futures. "They're having to tighten margin requirements.
